detaileddescription.para:
Key features are listed below, hardware details can be found into datasheet:

Supply voltage (recommended): 7V ~ 12V;

Supply voltage (limits): 6V ~ 20V;

Operating voltage: 5V;

Microcontroller: ATmega2560;

Digital I/O pins: 54 (of which 15 provide PWM output);

Analog input pins: 16;

DC Current per I/O Pin: 20 mA;

DC Current for 3.3V Pin: 50 mA;

Flash memory: 256Kb (8Kb used by bootloader);

SRAM: 8Kb;

EEPROM: 4Kb;

CPU clock: 16MHz;
